  %pSo John gotted his palsma rifle and blew up the wall.
  %p “HE GOING TO KILL US” said the demons
  %p “I will shoot at him” said the cyberdemon and he fired the rocket missiles. John plasmaed at him and tried to blew him up. But then the ceiling fell and they were trapped and not able to kill.
